# TypeScript & Zod

## Schemas

- Raw API shapes: `lib/schemas/omdb.ts`
- App DTOs: example `lib/schemas/movie.ts`, `lib/schemas/favorites.ts`
- Export inferred types: `export type Foo = z.infer<typeof fooSchema>`

## Validation

```typescript
// Route handlers — safeParse + 400 response
const parsed = movieSearchParamsSchema.safeParse(input);
if (!parsed.success) {
  return NextResponse.json(
    { error: parsed.error.issues[0]?.message },
    { status: 400 },
  );
}

// Server fetch — parse throws on invalid data
return omdbSearchResponseSchema.parse(json);
```

## Types

- Prefer `type` over `interface` for DTOs
- No `any` — use `unknown` + Zod parse at boundaries
- Import types with `import type { ... }`
